class app.db.model.CarModel(**kwargs)[source]

Bases: Model

Represents a car model.

Parameters:

  • id (int) – The unique identifier of the car model.

  • registration (str) – The registration number of the car model.

  • vin (str) – The VIN (Vehicle Identification Number) of the car model.

  • make (str) – The make of the car model.

  • model (str) – The model of the car model.

  • first_registration_date (date) – The date of the first registration of the car model.

  • production_year (str) – The production year of the car model.

  • mileage (str) – The current mileage of the car model.

  • fuel_consumption (str) – The fuel consumption of the car model.

  • fuel_type_id (int) – The foreign key referencing the fuel type of the car model.

  • vehicle_status_id (int) – The foreign key referencing the vehicle status of the car model.

Returns:

An instance of CarModel.
